<h1 class="text-center">Welcome to our carpet store!</h1>
<hr>
<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
    <div class="col-md-4 how-img">
        <img src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/persian-carpet-texture-21684751.jpg" class="rounded-circle img-fluid" alt="" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h4>We are the first machine made carpet factory in Bulgaria!</h4>
        <p class="text-muted">
            Оur company was established in 2019 in Sliven, Bulgaria.
