            We have awards from many carpet exhibitions, and currently we are the most selling company in our country!
        </p>
        <div class="text-end">
            <a class="btn btn-dark my-2" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="All" role="button">Products</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>